label: ItemListOrderType
comment: Enumerated for values for itemListOrder for indicating how an ordered ItemList is organized.

enumerationMembers.label: ItemListOrderAscending
enumerationMembers.comment: An ItemList ordered with lower values listed first.

enumerationMembers.label: ItemListOrderDescending
enumerationMembers.comment: An ItemList ordered with higher values listed first.

enumerationMembers.label: ItemListUnordered
enumerationMembers.comment: An ItemList ordered with no explicit order.
